Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.72,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:09.12,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:12.38,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You're back at the head of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.88,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried with your grades dropping there for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:17.95,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like you've straightened out your act.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.82,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because entrance exams are looming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:26.05,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it's thanks to the disappearance of that impediment to your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.47,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:54.90,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought they'd agree to open up the roof, but they went right for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:59.36,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard a third-year thug was monopolizing the key up 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:03.33,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bon'taro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.84,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm playing volleyball with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.25,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,How about joining in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.54,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Bontaro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:20.01,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're lonely without Kawabuchi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.98,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,but you've got to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.33,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.57,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're looking for Nishimi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.71,ED-Romaji,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\bord0\shad0\pos(336,171)\fscx37.5\fscy53.75\c&H99C1E1&}Shirayuri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.71,ED-Romaji,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\bord0\shad0\fscx35\fscy53.75\pos(959,171)\c&H99C1E1&}Shirayuri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.71,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.76,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I love milkshakes when it starts getting cold outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.43,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ritsuko-san? Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:51.30,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you're worried about \NKawabuchi-kun after he disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, there's that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.30,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I know! It's Nishimi-san, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.19,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Like, you haven't been able to talk at all or go home together recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.26,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, you can't just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.21,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,You need to make things happen yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.21,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.69,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Nishimi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Were you eating sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got whipped cream on your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:29.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.33,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're not coming to the basement today either?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,With entrance exams coming up, I've decided not to go for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Pops that I'm sorry for not being able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:44.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why not study at my place?
