Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The shop's closed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He's off buying up stock, so it's just me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:20.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That one's my favorite photos. I always have it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you look so happy in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Sentaro's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,English and math, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So first of all, the word order is reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:47.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This "so" comes first, and the subject and verb change places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:55.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:05:01.78,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking about how you felt when I showed you that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:07.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Since Sentaro left, you're the one it's hit the hardest, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:10.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:14.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He may not be around, but I've still got you, Ricchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, w-wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can be alone with you whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy that Sentaro is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're joking, I don't want to hear such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:44.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, I haven't been able to say this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm going to a college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home for today.
