Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.25,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't call Kawabuchi-kun's name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's going their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all forget being here in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.56,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:49.57,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever forget your performance at the school festival last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.28,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.57,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:59.37,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have the second button on your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.67,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if you'd be satisfied with mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.48,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.92,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure if I'd be able to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.96,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I was crying my eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.01,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.50,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell and good riddance to this damned slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.74,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go trudging up the thing tomorrow out of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.80,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.91,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going off to college in Tokyo too, Prince Bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.56,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll probably get a little lonely around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.18,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, we can't get gloomy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.56,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's great news, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.53,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:06.82,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko was accepted at the college here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.57,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ritsuko! Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:14.23,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Bon got into college! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan! You can stay there, but just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:31.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You may not want to hear anything from me, but just let me say this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:37.12,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I started coming here is because I wanted to see your smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:42.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, your smile always encouraged me, even when things were rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew that feeling before meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ricchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting you was a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.50,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Call us as soon as you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.13,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun, write me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.90,Background Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:23.09,Background Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,The sleeper express train, Sakura, will depart for Tokyo on track one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:25.54,Background Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Its next stop will be Haiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.86,Background Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,All passengers, please board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.31,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.98,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.69,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a little going-away gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is Ricchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:44.66,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. But there's a lunch in there that Ritsuko made for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.68,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care, Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I will. You too, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.82,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
