Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When you're sick, you're apt to lose heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but sickness and health start with the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:10.61,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, you have a good head on your shoulders for someone so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:13.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I'm still a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.30,Main Dialog,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Nishimi, we've got an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:45.40,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a free bed in the nap room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.95,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get a little rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:51.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, if I lie down now, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:59.34,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, being a resident on the night shift is even harder than I heard it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.56,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a lot of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:02.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:09.47,Main Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,Our guest is a popular star who both sings and acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.24,Main Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka Seiji-san joins us in the studio today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.23,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hello! I'm Matsuoka Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.23,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\bord2.5\fs88\pos(628,477)\c&HFCF9FB&\3c&H221E1E&}Guest: Matsuoka Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.15,Background Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,I want to start right off with a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:21.41,Background Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you like better, singing or acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.38,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.75,Background Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I like them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...a classmate from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:27.96,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My little sister goes nuts over that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.76,Background Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,And I like jazz too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.76,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get me an autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.58,Background Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jazz?!{wonder where he picked that up from?...lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:41.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Matsuoka's dream came true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.82,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:56.44,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.81,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:04.40,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful! You've become a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.37,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm six months along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:12.04,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi-san wants a girl, but I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.20,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'd spoil her rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:18.45,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,How are you? Have you been good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.83,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:26.72,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that Sentaro-kun had taken off, but you've never seen him since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.47,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.96,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:38.39,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been carrying around to show everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:42.06,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,A friend from back home sent me this photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:45.31,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but don't you think the person on the far left looks like someone we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Can I borrow this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:11.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been trying to forget him all this time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my heart is beating fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:19.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I can stop this rhythm in my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.11,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,If you want the church, it's at the top of the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.17,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,Young priest? Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:30.61,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The priest here has been around for years and years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:35.38,Main Dialog,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think he helps raise the orphans from around the prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He raises children?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:40.97,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you mean the priest-in-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:45.03,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Though I hear he does nothing but cause trouble for the poor priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.96,Main Dialog,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.25,Main Dialog,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Pick me up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.69,Main Dialog,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:59.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought this day might come sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.16,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.11,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,What do you two think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:45.48,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you can only play on special occasions, but again, you do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.53,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! Run, Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Sen!
